name: Sui RWA
description: Sui RWA is centered on an AI-powered investment ecosystem built on the Sui blockchain. Its core product is a suite of AI agents designed to analyze and trade tokenized real-world assets (e.g., real estate, equities, commodities). Users can select and customize these agents based on individual risk profiles and goals. Sui RWA will release an AI Agent platform that supports tokenized investments into RWA assets.
